Date: Thu, 17 Apr 2003 19:47:12 +0200
From: Martin Haditsch <martin.haditsch@travel-clinic.at>

I wouldn't dare to have doubts about the identification of this bug;
nevertheless it's well known that contact with soil and multidrug
resistance are also key indicators of _Ochrobactrum anthropi_. Did
you exclude rule out this option?
--
M. Haditsch
<martin.haditsch@travel-clinic.at>
